{
  "text": "Primary urethral squamous cell carcinoma (SCC) is a rare entity accounting for less than 1% of all cancers [CITATION_1] . Management of urethral cancer is a particularly challenging field owing to the paucity of evidence from randomised trials to inform practice.",
